ref>{{cite news|last1=Whaley|first1=Monte|title=Cynthia Coffman easily wins Colorado AG's race|url=http://www.denverpost.com/election2014/ci_26865418/coffman-winning-ags-race |work=The Denver Post |date=November 4, 2014 |accessdate=December 5, 2014}}</ref> They filed for divorce in June 2017.<ref>{{cite news|last1=Paul|first1=jesse|title=Cynthia and Mike Coffman have filed for divorce after 12 years of marriage|url=http://www.denverpost.com/2017/06/19/cynthia-mike-coffman-divorce|work=The Denver Post |date=June 20, 2017 |accessdate=June 20, 2017}}</ref>\n\nCoffman is a [[United Methodist Church|United Methodist]].<ref name=CampaignSite2008_About>{{cite web |url=http://www.coffmanforcongress.com/about.htm |title=About Mike Coffman |publisher=Mike Coffman for Congress |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080724162603/http://www.coffmanforcongress.com/about.htm |archivedate=July 24, 2008 }}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist|30em}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{Dmoz|Regional/North_America/United_States/Colorado/Government/Federal/US_House_of_Representatives/Mike_Coffman_%5BR-6%5D}}\n* {{C-SPAN|Mike Coffman}}\n* {{CongLinks | congbio = C001077 | votesmart = 1535 | fec = H8CO06138 | congress = mike-coffman/1912}}\n* [http://www.ontheissues.org/House/Mike_Coffman.htm Mike Coffman at On the Issues]\n\n{{s-start}}\n{{s-par|us-co-hs}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Bill Owens (Colorado politician)|Bill Owens]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=Member of the [[Colorado House of Representatives]]<br>from the 49th district|years=1989\u20131993}}\n{{s-aft|after=William H. Jerke}}\n|-\n{{s-bef|before=Jeanne W. Adkins}}\n{{s-ttl|title=Member of the [[Colorado House of Representatives]]<br>from the 40th district|years=1993\u20131994}}\n{{s-aft|after=Gary McPherson}}\n|-\n{{s-par|us-co-sen}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Bill Owens (Colorado politician)|Bill Owens]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=Member of the [[Colorado Senate]]<br>from the 27th district|years=1994\u20131999}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[John Andrews (Colorado p